html: <amexio-form form-name='validateForm' header='true' show-error='true'> <amexio-form-header> Registration Form </amexio-form-header> <amexio-form-body> <amexio-row> <amexio-column [size]='6'> <amexio-text-input [min-length]='3' [(ngModel)]='firstName' [max-length]='5' [allow-blank]='false' field-label='First Name' name='firstName' place-holder='Enter first name' icon-feedback='true'> </amexio-text-input> </amexio-column> <amexio-column [size]='6'> <amexio-text-input field-label='Last Name' name='lastName' [(ngModel)]='lastName' place-holder='Enter last name(not mandatory)' allow-blank='true' error-msg='Please enter last name' [min-length]='3' min-error-msg='Minimum 3 char required' [max-length]='10' max-error-msg='Maximum 10 char allowed' icon-feedback='true'> </amexio-text-input> </amexio-column> </amexio-row> </amexio-form-body> <amexio-form-action> <amexio-button label='Save' type='primary' form-bind='validateForm'> </amexio-button> <amexio-button label='Cancel' type='theme-backgroundcolor'> </amexio-button> </amexio-form-action> </amexio-form>
